title: I'm in Love with the Villainess
subTitle: Rei Ohashi, an overworked employee, passes away after which she is reincarnated as Rae Taylor, her favourite video game's heroine, and gets attracted to Claire Francois, the main antagonist.
Jackson Curtis, a discontented writer, battles against all odds to keep his family secure when a series of apocalyptic calamities threaten to decimate humankind.
A spaceship crash lands on prehistoric Earth, leaving only two survivors. Soon, they must survive against the hostile terrain and vicious creatures.

title: Money Train
subTitle: A revengeful New York City transit policeman resolves to rob a state-of-the-art train laden with lots of money. Meanwhile, his foster brother, who is also a policeman, endeavours to safeguard him.

title: Julie & Julia
subTitle: Julie Powell, a young blogger, is determined to emulate Julia Child's cooking techniques. Though separated by time, the two women share a common passion for food that intertwines their lives.

title: A-X-L
subTitle: Miles befriends A-X-L, a robotic dog, when he manages to activate its owner-pairing technology. However, Miles's life takes an unusual turn when A-X-L's creators come searching for it.

title: Bullet Train
subTitle: Ladybug, a professional assassin, is assigned to retrieve a briefcase from a bullet train. Soon, he finds himself battling many other killers who board the same train but with a different objective.

title: Kung Fu Hustle
subTitle: An aspiring gangster pretends to be part of a notorious gang and tries to terrorise a neighbourhood. However, unknown to him, three martial arts experts live there and are ready to take him down.

title: Escape Room
subTitle: Six people from different walks of life participate in an escape room competition to win ten thousand dollars. Things change when they find themselves in horrifying circumstances.

title: Escape Room: Tournament of Champions
subTitle: Ben and Zoey find themselves trapped in a series of deadly escape rooms with four others. They try to survive and find a way out as they slowly discover that they have played the game before.

title: You Don't Mess With the Zohan
subTitle: Zohan, an Israeli anti-terrorist commando, stages his own death when he gets tired of his job and goes to New York City to follow his dream of being a hairstylist.

title: Kill 'Em All 2
subTitle: Partnered by the CIA, Phillip and Vanessa return to Europe, facing a vengeful Russian-French terrorist Vlad, who wants to settle the score for his dead brother.

title: Gran Turismo
subTitle: With the help of a mechanic having a tragic past, an avid player of racing video games attempts to become a professional car racer.

title: Godzilla
subTitle: The fallout of a military nuclear test causes an iguana to mutate into a giant monster. Now this monster lays waste to cannery ships and New York city in order to feed and protect its brood.

subTitle: After a girl with hearing impairment envisions the Virgin Mary and regains her ability to hear along with other powers, a journalist unravels the truth behind this paranoia.

title: The Equalizer

title: Monster Hunter
